{
  "3263410": {
    "name": "我的废土日记",
    "steam_appid": 3263410,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/4a3c1ad2157fdac512761fb9b85eddd0.avif?t=1758856584\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras_big/4a3c1ad2157fdac512761fb9b85eddd0.avif?t=1758856584 width=800 height=135 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       在近未来的废土世界里，资源匮乏、危机四伏。你将扮演一名幸存者，在开放世界中搜集资源、打造装备，探索生存之道。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/c26e1f30b118809ff9aa1d2f8974042b.poster.avif?t=1758856584\" width=800 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/c26e1f30b118809ff9aa1d2f8974042b.webm?t=1758856584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/c26e1f30b118809ff9aa1d2f8974042b.mp4?t=1758856584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       在这里，你会遇到一些同样生存在这片废土上的NPC。你可以选择合作或是对抗、是帮助弱小还是掠夺他人……每一个决定都将塑造你独一无二的废土历程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/b2e67c03a43c05f674fce8d20f501554.avif?t=1758856584\" width=800 height=132 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       游戏中，将随机生成各色NPC：他们会根据自己的需求和经历作出决策，比如合作、交易、复仇或掠夺。每个NPC都可能成为你的盟友或敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/a2403ad8f8687d492334ca7f6c50d07a.poster.avif?t=1758856584\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/a2403ad8f8687d492334ca7f6c50d07a.webm?t=1758856584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/a2403ad8f8687d492334ca7f6c50d07a.mp4?t=1758856584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/af9292853e272c585b1a6de4d2771cfb.avif?t=1758856584\" width=800 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       你将在无缝开放的地图中：自由探索资源点、参与交易、打造装备；你可以创建势力成为首领，或加入NPC阵营效忠强者——用智慧与武力践行你的末日法则。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/f306ca538a82eaf697be7b256e3bea45.poster.avif?t=1758856584\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/f306ca538a82eaf697be7b256e3bea45.webm?t=1758856584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/f306ca538a82eaf697be7b256e3bea45.mp4?t=1758856584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/519de13fc9792f1804ff9c619f46bc05.avif?t=1758856584\" width=800 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        实时战斗系统，需要你恰当搭配自己与NPC伙伴的武器与装备，以战胜不同的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/c5e6dcb0e10bcfe35c9bdaeb346abf4d.poster.avif?t=1758856584\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/c5e6dcb0e10bcfe35c9bdaeb346abf4d.webm?t=1758856584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/c5e6dcb0e10bcfe35c9bdaeb346abf4d.mp4?t=1758856584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/4bb5b26720765d88427e7aab3fa438ce.avif?t=1758856584\" width=800 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       除了从敌对势力资源点盗取物资外，你还需要洞察供需关系导致的市场变化，在资源稀缺的废土世界中找到最佳生存策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/cf74cb7127bb4df4d1dcfdc2436da6ad.poster.avif?t=1758856584\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/cf74cb7127bb4df4d1dcfdc2436da6ad.webm?t=1758856584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/cf74cb7127bb4df4d1dcfdc2436da6ad.mp4?t=1758856584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/d703872c5d0a6e0c7ba72a2bfbac002e.avif?t=1758856584\" width=800 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       通过探索与跑商换取材料，制作高级装备，保障自己与伙伴的生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/15fd43b732773b172ea9f09bc66d53e5.poster.avif?t=1758856584\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/15fd43b732773b172ea9f09bc66d53e5.webm?t=1758856584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263410/extras/15fd43b732773b172ea9f09bc66d53e5.mp4?t=1758856584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       现在，开始你的末日废土之路吧，勇士！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
